title: Steve Wilkos I Do Dope With Daddy
description:
I DO DOPE WITH DADDY:
---------------------
    Father-Daughter bonding gone terribly wrong... Mariah's father and older sister are terribly addicted to heroin and painkillers. It's gotten so bad, she's had to witness cops busting in her door, people shooting at her house, and her sister prostituting for drugs. Mariah's had to live with it for all these years, but now she's out of hope, and Steve's her last chance. But can Steve be the one to finally stand up to her family and save them from a bleak future?

ENJOY PLEASE SEED AND SAY THANK YOU
